WEBVTT

33:41.620 --> 33:46.039
There are some foreigners also, I will just explain to you.

33:46.239 --> 33:50.068
Today is the day where, whatever you want to know

33:50.268 --> 33:57.179
of eternal nature, you can ask Me and will last for eternity.

33:57.379 --> 33:59.680
But many people think that today is the day

33:59.881 --> 34:04.965
where, whatever you ask, God has to give you. It’s true,

34:05.166 --> 34:11.404
whatever you ask, you’ll get it. But it’s just a temptation.

34:11.809 --> 34:17.595
Beyond that is eternity.

34:18.524 --> 34:20.855
So, whatever you have to ask,

34:21.072 --> 34:28.078
you should ask for something that is eternal, indestructible.

34:28.278 --> 34:34.239
That higher state

34:34.439 --> 34:43.671
which is called the permanent state of joy and bliss

34:43.871 --> 34:50.655
is to be asked today because all other askings are wasted

34:50.855 --> 34:54.957
and you again go back to the position where you were.

34:55.157 --> 35:01.048
It’s important to understand that this time, today,

35:01.248 --> 35:08.315
you have to ask something eternal for yourself,

35:08.515 --> 35:13.038
something eternal for your family,

35:13.238 --> 35:16.067
something eternal for your country

35:16.267 --> 35:22.678
and something eternal for this world and universe.

35:22.878 --> 35:29.733
You all are Sahaja Yogis and of a very high level

35:29.933 --> 35:43.856
and I’m happy that the whole of you have come here

35:44.056 --> 35:51.138
for that eternal state of Devi.

35:51.338 --> 35:58.385
And if it works out,

35:58.585 --> 36:03.813
you should get that eternal state within yourself.

36:04.013 --> 36:10.740
You should get that state where you don’t want anything anymore

36:10.940 --> 36:16.604
and reside in that beautiful condition

36:16.804 --> 36:25.429
of complete peace and bliss.

36:26.937 --> 36:38.165
That’s what is available to you and you can easily achieve it.

36:38.365 --> 36:41.292
I cannot say this to people who are not Sahaja Yogis.

36:41.492 --> 36:45.568
But I can definitely say this to people who are Sahaja Yogis

36:45.768 --> 36:56.750
and who have achieved already Self-realization.

36:58.162 --> 37:02.548
So, today, I hope you, all of you will pray

37:02.748 --> 37:13.212
and ask for that eternal love of God.

37:13.412 --> 37:19.181
It should flow to you all the time.

37:19.381 --> 37:24.380
May God bless you all.
